Package org.microbean.type

Class InvariantTypeSemantics

java.lang.Object
org.microbean.type.TypeSemantics
org.microbean.type.InvariantTypeSemantics
@Experimental
public abstract class InvariantTypeSemantics
extends TypeSemantics
An abstract TypeSemantics that, in general, compares Types using invariant semantics.

Normally WildcardType instances would be compared using covariant semantics so often subclasses will override the TypeSemantics.getSemanticsFor(Type, Type) appropriately.

Author:
Laird Nelson
See Also:
CovariantTypeSemantics, TypeSemantics
